OL,3,CWrong body cremated in 'heartbreaking'
OL,4,Cmix up at the Grange University
OL,5,CHospital in Cwmbran
OL,7,FNHS officials have apologised to a
OL,8,Fbereaved family after they attended a
OL,9,Fcremation for the wrong body.
OL,11,FThe family had to attended a second
OL,12,Fcremation after the error was
OL,13,Fdiscovered at the Grange University
OL,14,FHospital in Cwmbran, it has been
OL,15,Freported.
OL,17,FThe chief executive of the board that
OL,18,Fruns the hospital said staff have been
OL,19,Fleft "utterly heartbroken" by the mix-
OL,20,Fup.
